{"tid":1971444,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"的士撞冧交通燈　燈箱飛彈至數米外","createTime":"2020-04-14T02:07:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-14T02:31:47.000Z","uid":3090,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2e7168a977a72189f32bf1aca84a5cab87aa802d","tid":1971444,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T02:07:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D45cUYE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD45cUYE.jpg&h=6f668c0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n尖沙咀發生交通意外。今早(14日)6時44分，一名姓陳(51歲)司機駕駛的士沿科學館道往東行，至新東海商業中心對開時，失事撞冧交通燈及兩個交通燈箱，交通燈被撞至傾斜，燈箱亦飛彈至數米外，的士車頭撞至摺起損毀，幸事件中無人受傷，意外原因有待警方進一步調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200414/mobile/bkn-20200414073849541-0414_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200414%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20200414073849541-0414_00822_001.html&d=lExWnqkLii2%2BVYlrfbo%2B8wfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=81406349\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200414/mobile/bkn-20200414073849541-0414_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"de8fa806e834d2a54857ce72665bffba42dca74d","tid":1971444,"uid":74622,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T02:08:22.000Z","msg":"用愛膚堅啦"},{"pid":"801eab51646a1ad170a1c33fbf97d76f523bc204","tid":1971444,"uid":59920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T02:08:35.000Z","msg":"on9 dc9<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bf4ad5ef3c9182578270faee3b0a2d732faa428","tid":1971444,"uid":50101,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T02:31:47.000Z","msg":"早排先幫街邊電箱又裝鐵籠又盛，點知的士狗一嘢就KO你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class